  <section id="Section575005">
    <title><anchor id="Anchor575004" role="Index"
    xreflabel="opportunities:types for" /> <indexterm significance="normal"
        zone="Anchor575261">
        <primary>opportunities</primary>

        <secondary>creating new types for</secondary>
      </indexterm>Opportunity Type</title>

    <para id="Para575262">To create a new Opportunity Type, select the NEW
    button. The following screen will appear:</para>

    <para id="Para575266"><screenshot>
        <mediaobject>
          <imageobject>
            <imagedata fileref="images/CRM_MI_optyTypesNew.png"
                       id="Graphic575264" />
          </imageobject>

          <caption id="Caption575267">Create New Opportunity Type</caption>
        </mediaobject>
      </screenshot></para>

    <para id="Para575268">When creating a new Opportunity Type, you are
    presented with the following options:</para>

    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para575269">Name</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1848f58">
          <para>Enter a name to define the Opportunity Type.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para575270">Description</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1848fa0">
          <para>Enter a brief description of the Opportunity Type.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>

    <para id="Para575271">To the far right of the screen, the following
    buttons are available:</para>

    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para575272">CANCEL</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x184900c">
          <para>Closes the screen without creating an Opportunity Type,
          returning you to the previous screen.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para575273">SAVE</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1849054">
          <para>Creates the Opportunity Type and adds it to the master list of
          Opportunity Types.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>
  </section>